# Third-Party Licenses

`waft` is distributed under the MIT License (see [LICENSE](LICENSE)).

This file is auto-generated by `cargo about generate` and lists the
licenses of the third-party crates statically linked into the `waft`
binary. Build-time and dev-time dependencies (test runners, benchmark
harnesses, proc-macro inputs) are excluded.

To regenerate: `just regen-licenses`. CI fails if this file is out of
date relative to `Cargo.lock`.

